headline: Starbucks Files CEO Pay Drop as Turnaround Takes Shape
summary: Brian Niccol's fiscal 2025 compensation fell to $31 million as shares declined and performance-based awards were limited.

headline: Earnings Preview: Chipotle Mexican Grill (CMG) Q4 Earnings Expected to Decline
summary: Chipotle (CMG) doesn't possess the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely earnings beat in its upcoming report. Get prepared with the key expectations.

headline: Rallyday Partners Welcomes Haley Rushing as Purpose and Culture Architect
summary: DENVER, January 27, 2026--Renowned ‘Purposologist’, Haley Rushing, Joins Rallyday to Help Executive Teams Build Scalable and Impactful Organizations

headline: CHIPOTLE KICKS OFF 2026 MENU INNOVATION WITH THE RETURN OF CHICKEN AL PASTOR, ONE OF ITS MOST REQUESTED ITEMS
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced that it is bringing back Chicken al Pastor to restaurants in the U.S., Canada, the UK, France and Germany for a limited time starting Tuesday, February 10. The fan-favorite returns as Chipotle accelerates its 2026 menu innovation schedule with three to four limited-time protein offerings as well as new sides and dips.

headline: Chipotle bets Chicken al Pastor will bring consumers back
summary: The fast casual giant is increasing the frequency of its protein LTOs in a bid to drive trial, relevance and traffic.

headline: Starbucks CEO Brian Niccol Earned $31 Million in 2025
summary: Niccol’s 2025 pay includes a $5 million bonus and nearly $20 million in stock awards, according to a filing from the coffee chain on Monday.  The stock awards will be based in part on company performance.
